background:
In a survey to identify the level of public concern regarding two environmental topics (genetically modified food and intensive pesticide use), 20 people were asked to score their level of concern on a scale from 1 (not concerned at all) to 5 (very concerned). The results obtained were:

\begin{tabular}{lllllllllllllllllllll} 
Genetically modified food & 5 & 1 & 1 & 4 & 3 & 3 & 4 & 5 & 2 & 3 & 5 & 4 & 3 & 2 & 1 & 5 & 1 & 2 & 2 & 3 \\
Intensive pesticide use & 2 & 1 & 2 & 1 & 1 & 2 & 3 & 1 & 2 & 3 & 3 & 1 & 2 & 1 & 1 & 1 & 1 & 1 & 1 & 2 \\
\hline
\end{tabular}
